


### Perini p. 128

1 medium cucumber
* 4 ripe tomatoes
* 1 clove garlic
* 1/3 cup minced onion
* 1/2 cup minced bell pepper
* 1/4 cup olive oil
* 2 cups tomato juice
* 1 t salt
* dash of pepper
* 1 T vinegar

* Dice cucumber and tomatoes
* Blend all ingredients for 1 minute
* chill for at least 4 hours
